elly-Christine-Sutton.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit-Kelly-Christine-Sutton-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit-Kelly-Christine-Sutton-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit-Kelly-Christine-Sutton-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit-Kelly-Christine-Sutton-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves.-Credit-Kelly-Christine-Sutton-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/kacey-musgraves">Kacey Musgraves</a>分享了她的最新单曲《Too Good To Be True》，并宣布了 2024 年英国、欧洲和美国巡演的详细信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/kacey-musgraves-star-crossed-review-3040734">凯西·马斯格雷夫斯（Kacey Musgraves）——《星辰变》评论：对心碎的有力而诚实的描述</a></strong></li></ul><p>《Too Good To Be True》是七届格莱美奖得主创作歌手即将发行的唱片《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kacey-musgraves-announces-new-album-deeper-well-and-shares-leads-single-3584616">Deeper Well》</a>中发行的第二首单曲。该曲目紧随<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kacey-musgraves-announces-new-album-deeper-well-and-shares-leads-single-3584616">同名主打单曲</a>之后。</p><p>马斯格雷夫斯在这首民谣中唱出了脆弱和遗憾，在柔和的吉他连复段中唱出了“<em>对我好，我也会对你好/但请不要好得令人难以置信</em>”。 </p><p><iframe title="Kacey Musgraves - 好得令人难以置信（官方歌词视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zSIGEn11V6E?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>她的第六张录音室唱片将于 3 月 15 日通过 Interscope/MCA Nashville 发行，并可<a href="https://kaceymusgraves.komi.io/">在此处预存/预订</a>。</p><p> 《Deeper Well》是继她 2021 年专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/kacey-musgraves-star-crossed-review-3040734">Star-Crossed</a> 》之后推出的。 《NME》在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/kacey-musgraves-star-crossed-review-3040734">对该专辑的四星评论</a>中<em>写道</em>：“这张唱片以其多样的声音和残酷诚实的歌词，从未发现马斯格雷夫斯回避了不舒服的地方。这是一个复杂的项目——这张唱片还附有一部 50 分钟的电影——可能会在其概念的重压下崩溃。然而，在作者坦率的笔下，并灌输了希望感，这是一次强有力的聆听。”</p><p>在发行《Too Good To Be True》的同时，马斯格雷夫斯还宣布将于 4 月 28 日星期日在都柏林 3Olympia 剧院开始 2024 年世界巡演，巡演地点包括美国、英国和欧洲。</p><p>马迪·迪亚兹、约翰·米斯蒂神父、休伦勋爵和尼克·克里克将在选定的日期提供支持。</p><p>门票预售将于当地时间 3 月 5 日星期二上午 10 点至当地时间 3 月 7 日星期四晚上 10 点向所有美国运通卡会员开放。一般门票销售将于当地时间 3 月 8 日星期五上午 10 点开始。访问此处获取<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fkacey-musgraves-tickets%2Fartist%2F1668663" target="_blank" rel="noopener">英国和欧洲门票</a>，访问此处获取<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fkacey-musgraves-tickets%2Fartist%2F1668663" target="_blank" rel="noopener">美国门票</a>。查看下面的完整巡演日期列表。 </p><figure id="attachment_3594984" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3594984" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3594984" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves-Deeper-Well-2024-world-tour-dates.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="凯西·马斯格雷夫斯“Deeper Well”2024 年世界巡演日期。信用出版社" width="2000" height="2500" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves-Deeper-Well-2024-world-tour-dates.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves-Deeper-Well-2024-world-tour-dates.-Credit-PRESS-400x500.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves-Deeper-Well-2024-world-tour-dates.-Credit-PRESS-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves-Deeper-Well-2024-world-tour-dates.-Credit-PRESS-696x870.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves-Deeper-Well-2024-world-tour-dates.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1740.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Kacey-Musgraves-Deeper-Well-2024-world-tour-dates.-Credit-PRES