 Charli XCX 分享俱乐部准备的新单曲“Von Dutch” https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-shares-club-ready-new-single-von-dutch-3594986?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=charli-xcx-shares-club-ready-新单冯荷兰语Anagricel DuranThu, 29 Feb 2024 17:53:07 +0000 Music NewsNewsdancePophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3594986 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Charli-XCX-Von-Dutch-single-artwork.-Credit-Terrence-OConnor.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Charli XCX &#39;Von Dutch&#39; 单一艺术品。图片来源：泰伦斯·奥康纳" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Charli-XCX-Von-Dutch-single-artwork.-Credit-Terrence-OConnor.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Charli-XCX-Von-Dutch-single-artwork.-Credit-Terrence-OConnor-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Charli-XCX-Von-Dutch-single-artwork.-Credit-Terrence-OConnor-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Charli-XCX-Von-Dutch-single-artwork.-Credit-Terrence-OConnor-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Charli-XCX-Von-Dutch-single-artwork.-Credit-Terrence-OConnor-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Charli-XCX-Von-Dutch-single-artwork.-Credit-Terrence-OConnor-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌标志着她的新专辑“Brat”中发行的第一首单曲</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-shares-club-ready-new-single-von-dutch-3594986">Charli XCX 分享俱乐部准备的新单曲“Von Dutch”</a>后首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Charli-XCX-Von-Dutch-single-artwork.-Credit-Terrence-OConnor.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Charli XCX &#39;Von Dutch&#39; 单一艺术品。图片来源：泰伦斯·奥康纳" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Charli-XCX-Von-Dutch-single-artwork.-Credit-Terrence-OConnor.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Charli-XCX-Von-Dutch-single-artwork.-Credit-Terrence-OConnor-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Charli-XCX-Von-Dutch-single-artwork.-Credit-Terrence-OConnor-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Charli-XCX-Von-Dutch-single-artwork.-Credit-Terrence-OConnor-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Charli-XCX-Von-Dutch-single-artwork.-Credit-Terrence-OConnor-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Charli-XCX-Von-Dutch-single-artwork.-Credit-Terrence-OConnor-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>发行了她的俱乐部新歌“Von Dutch”，这是她即将发行的专辑“Brat”中的第一首单曲。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/charli-xcx-cover-interview-2022-crash-3337132">Charli XCX 接受采访：“我喜欢用流行音乐玩游戏。我喜欢拿它开玩笑”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首歌由 Easyfun 制作，是一首合成器重的曲子，XCX 在轻快的节奏中过着“<em>邪教经典但我仍然流行”</em>的生活。</p><p>由托索执导，冯·达奇的伴奏音乐视频以查理在巴黎戴高乐机场被狗仔队包围开始。从那里，她一边挣扎一边试图逃离镜头，登上了飞机。</p><p>她 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-previews-new-song-von-dutch-on-tiktok-3582070">此前在社交媒体上分享了这首歌的 20 秒片段</a>，并于上周在纽约市最近的 Boiler Room 演出中演唱了这首歌。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Charli XCX - Von dutch（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cwZ1L_0QLjw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这首歌是她即将推出的第六张专辑“Brat”中发行的第一首单曲。本周， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-teases-new-album-brat-3594361">XCX 分享了这张专辑的艺术作品，并且该专辑将于今年夏天以“15 首歌曲”的形式发行</a>。 41:23 分钟长，重复。”</p><p> XCX 此前曾<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-reveals-new-album-is-a-dance-record-following-boiler-room-appearance-3592301">暗示，她即将推出的新专辑是一张舞曲唱片，这可以追溯到她对俱乐部音乐的根源</a>。